tempat tanpa CCTV.

291
00:16:47,617 --> 00:16:48,617
Dia tidak tertangkap di CCTV...

292
00:16:48,617 --> 00:16:49,658
...dan masuk ke kantor.

293
00:16:49,918 --> 00:16:51,558
